metadata.name: Shackled in colors
metadata.description:
Portrait of "Shackled in colors" from a series of modern photographs.

The portrait personifies the inner colors of the soul, our thoughts and pressing problems.

Made with flash light on camera Canon EOS 6DM2 + Sigma 85mm F/1.4 DG DN | ART

New owner will get 3863  x  5795 png file.
